Class FluentElementFilter<T extends Element>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.holisticon.annotationprocessortoolkit.filter.FluentElementFilter<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - 

    public final class FluentElementFilter<T extends Element>
extends Object
    Fluent filter utility class to filter lists of Elements. Each filter operation produces a FluentElementFilter instance.
